snippet.title: Dear You - Higurashi vocal Drum and Bass remix
snippet.description:
I've finally set up a paypal donate button on my main page and a sendspace link to the HQ mp3 file. 

I'm not going to demand anyone pay to download the mp3, but I hope enough of my fans support me financially, so I can spend less time working and more time making music! Even 1 dollar/pound/euro is really appreciated.

Here's the link, let me know when i need to re-upload.

https://www.sendspace.com/file/y931tp

and here's a link to my soundcloud page

https://soundcloud.com/adam-whitton/dear-you-higurashi-vocal-dnb

Check it out and please leave me a comment, if you liked this then you might like my other drum and bass remixes.

Thanks for Listening guys
